            . I lost a handkerchief, which I had put<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183106300106"></xptr>on the prisoner's bed - I asked him for it; he said he did not know any thing about it - I afterwards saw it in his hand, and called an officer who took him; this is the handkerchief - there had been a crown-piece in the corner of it, but that is gone.</p>
